-*- outline -*-

* Img2Epub installation


** Posix (Linux, Cygwin, ...)

Python, 7zip and ImageMagick must be previously installed

go inside img2epub extracted folder and run:

./install.sh for usr/local

or

PREFIX=PATH ./install.sh


** Windows

Python, 7zip and ImageMagick must be previously installed and in system or user
Path.

Copy img2epub extracted folder where you want (for example C:\Program Files)

to launch it open cmd shell and run

python "C:\Program Files\img2epub\img2epub" --help
